AROS web site too slow ? Now you can mirror us with

<shell>    rsync -avz --delete rsync://www.aros.org/aroswww www</shell>

Don't forget to tell us the link of your mirror so we can mention
you in the links section :-) The first mirror is at
<a href="http://aros.planetmirror.com">http://aros.planetmirror.com</a>.

And 4play has created an IRC channel for us on
<a href="http://www.efnet.org/index.php">EFNet</a>.
<shell>/join #aros</shell>, the official AROS IRC channel.
